Web Service / API :
https://www.amazon.com/s?k=iphone&crid=3OEHIBEJ6UNN2&sprefix=iphone%2Caps%2C78&ref=nb_sb_noss_1
 - BaseURL - https://www.amazon.com
 - endpoint - /s
Resource locator - 
 - Query Params = value
k=iphone
crid=3OEHIBEJ6UNN2
sprefix=iphone%2Caps%2C78
ref=nb_sb_noss_1

Request:
 - HTTP Methods - POST, PUT, GET, DELETE
 CURD - Create, Update, Read, Delete
 - URL : Base URL + Endpoints + Resource Locator
 - Payload / Request Body : POST, PUT, DELETE (Optinal), (GET do not required a payload), empty body {}
 - Request Header
 - Query Params (Optional)
 
Response:
 - Response Code / HTTP Status Code
 200 - 200-299 : 200 Success, 201 Successfully Created, 204 No Content
 300 - 300-399 : Redirecting
 400 - 400-499 : Client Side error, 404 Not Found
 500 - 500-599 : Server Side error, 504 Server unavailable
 - Response Body (Optional)
 - Response Header
